Wednesday, February 10,1999

MERIT DOCKET

99-265. State v. Lantz.

Perry App. No. 9763. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal and claimed appeal of right. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for stay of court of appeals’ judgment entry,

*1494IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed as moot.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
